{"tid":1929334,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"武漢肺炎疫情下 「洋蝗」「土蝗」聯攻 中國急布預防","createTime":"2020-03-17T01:20:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-17T01:30:22.000Z","uid":29188,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"dff6d75114793b4f8cf2483ea93a7aeb62b6f817","tid":1929334,"uid":29188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T01:20:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://s.rfi.fr/media/display/2f90bba6-5cae-11ea-985c-005056bf87d6/w:900/p:16x9/2020-02-27T000000Z_1776590616_RC219F9SLHNL_RTRMADP_3_AFRICA-LOCUSTS.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.rfi.fr%2Fmedia%2Fdisplay%2F2f90bba6-5cae-11ea-985c-005056bf87d6%2Fw%3A900%2Fp%3A16x9%2F2020-02-27T000000Z_1776590616_RC219F9SLHNL_RTRMADP_3_AFRICA-LOCUSTS.JPG&h=0946e1f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">圖為2月21日，肯尼亞一位農民拚命驅趕飛到田地的大片蝗蟲。 REUTERS - Baz Ratner</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>沙漠蝗引發的災害肆虐非洲，蔓延巴基斯坦及印度等亞洲國家，據信逼近中國邊境。中國國家農業局和國家林業草原局已相繼發出沙漠蝗災害預警，並制定預案，防範境外&ldquo;洋蝗&rdquo;與境內&ldquo;土蝗&rdquo;。</strong><br />\n<br />\n據中央社今天報道說，土洋皆防，中國提蝗蟲預案控制損失5%以下。<br />\n<br />\n該報道引述中國央視新聞，中國農業農村部、海關總署、國家林草局近日制定&ldquo;沙漠蝗及國內蝗蟲監測防控預案&rdquo;，強調要&ldquo;禦蝗於境外、備戰於境內&rdquo;，既嚴防境外沙漠蝗入侵，又繼續做好國內蝗蟲防治。據預案表示，具體目標是總體危害損失率控制在5%以內。包括邊境地區沙漠蝗遷入風險點監測和防治處置率達到100%；國內飛蝗防治處置率達到90%，農牧區土蝗防治處置率達到80%。<br />\n<br />\n該預案說，要加強雲南、西藏、新疆等可能遷入區的監測、及時預警，按照遷入風險，設定50萬畝應急防治任務。配套組建專業防治隊伍，儲備應急防控物資，一旦遷飛入境，立即啟動應急防治。<br />\n<br />\n預案寫道，將按照發生程度，提升防治準備級別。高密度發生區準備化學應急防治，中低密度發生區用生物防治和生態控制，確保飛蝗不起飛成災、土蝗不擴散危害。<br />\n<br />\n該報道說，寧波晚報曾指，中方計畫派出一支為數10萬隻的&ldquo;鴨子軍隊&rdquo;到巴基斯坦滅蝗，主要&ldquo;戰力&rdquo;是名為&ldquo;國紹1號&rdquo;的鴨子。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20200315-%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E4%B8%8B-%E6%B4%8B%E8%9D%97-%E5%9C%9F%E8%9D%97-%E8%81%AF%E6%94%BB-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%80%A5%E5%B8%83%E9%A0%90%E9%98%B2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Ftw%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F20200315-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585%25E4%25B8%258B-%25E6%25B4%258B%25E8%259D%2597-%25E5%259C%259F%25E8%259D%2597-%25E8%2581%25AF%25E6%2594%25BB-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2580%25A5%25E5%25B8%2583%25E9%25A0%2590%25E9%2598%25B2&d=AC0Zr9jWFF2OJ189utQw8DMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=5ebadf59\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20200315-%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E4%B8%8B-%E6%B4%8B%E8%9D%97-%E5%9C%9F%E8%9D%97-%E8%81%AF%E6%94%BB-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%80%A5%E5%B8%83%E9%A0%90%E9%98%B2</a>"},{"pid":"ab43f880e4212f61506fef525619fe9e21a77a12","tid":1929334,"uid":187987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T01:23:59.000Z","msg":"又話可防可控? DLLM la!"},{"pid":"42d8f5ebfbdb6748825b21e646c3010430cbc18d","tid":1929334,"uid":49144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T01:24:52.000Z","msg":"可防可控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb612443bf4b303a88dfe5d0fc4108b68c0a8d9a","tid":1929334,"uid":56326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T01:26:39.000Z","msg":"八國聯軍外加吳三桂李自成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f720d600b6e98438e0203d85d6970bc5febdbab1","tid":1929334,"uid":20898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T01:27:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/srwzmR9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsrwzmR9.png&h=cae52ffd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"251ba7f34796435964ddcce2cdf0a1461cffafb2","tid":1929334,"uid":2521,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T01:27:40.000Z","msg":"班鴨仔兵可能未開始食蝗<br />\n就已經俾蝗食左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25ef0c42de81b7d340b46b63a384d950292b5710","tid":1929334,"uid":306614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab43f8